description:
The boys speak on the unjust murder of George Floyd, the repercussions for Derek Chauvin, and the systemic change that needs to take place in America. ALSO: Logan is burnt out and needs a break from YouTube, Mike has replaced drugs with late-night snacks, and Trump’s “Space Force” astronauts are trained to interact with aliens.
